/**
 * Msg attributes:
 *   - owner: github repo owner
 *   - repo: github repo name
 *   - payload: sha for which the commits are desired
 * 
 * Return:
 *   - payload: commits for sha
 * 
 * Source: https://docs.github.com/en/rest/git/commits?apiVersion=2022-11-28#get-a-commit-object
 */

